🇮🇳 QUEENIN 👑 ▫️
🚫The day before these pics were taken, India stopped issuing tourist visas.
▫️
🗺 Moments before these pics, we got news of the European travel ban (folks on our group trip connected thru EU to get here)
▫️
🕌 5 days after these pics, the Taj Mahal closed to the public.
▫️
🇺🇸 All of 50 of us got back safely to the States with a few inconveniences (health screenings, extra paperwork) but no MAJOR disruptions during what would be the beginning of countries closing their borders as corona evolved into a full-blown pandemic 🦠.
▫️
🙏 When I tell you this trip was blessed and highly favored, babayy I mean it!! We missed these bans and restrictions by days!!!! Shout out to  @nomadnesstribe and @evierobbie for holdin us down while we were 8,000 miles away from home.
▫️ ▫️
▫️
